{{expand|time=2014-10-01T06:46:20+00:00}}
'''硫代硫酸鹽-檸檬酸鹽-膽鹽-蔗糖洋菜培養基'''（Thiosulfate-citrate-bile salts-sucrose agar，簡稱'''TCBS培養基'''），也稱為'''弧菌選擇培養基'''，是一種用來檢驗[[弧菌屬|弧菌]]種類的[[培養基|培養基]]。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Pfeffer |first1=C. |last2=Oliver |first2=J.D. |year=2003 |title= A comparison of thiosulphate-citrate-bile salts-sucrose (TCBS) agar and thiosulphate-chloride-iodide (TCI) agar for the isolation of Vibrio species from estuarine environments |journal=Letters in Applied Microbiology |volume=36 |pmid=12581373 |issue=3 |pages=150–151 |url= |doi=10.1046/j.1472-765X.2003.01280.x}}</ref>無法[[發酵|發酵]][[蔗糖|蔗糖]]的細菌，例如[[腸炎弧菌|腸炎弧菌]]，在此培養基上的菌落顏色會呈現綠色；而能夠發酵蔗糖的細菌菌落則呈現黃色。TCBS培養基的主要成分是[[硫代硫酸鈉|硫代硫酸鈉]]、[[膽酸鈉|膽酸鈉]]、[[檸檬酸鈉|檸檬酸鈉]]和[[蔗糖|蔗糖]]。培养基还包含[[百里酚蓝|百里酚蓝]]和[[溴百里酚藍|溴百里酚藍]]作为[[pH指示剂|pH指示剂]]以显示培养细菌时的[[酸碱值|酸碱值]]变化。<ref name="tcbs">{{Cite web | url=http://www.merckmillipore.com/chemicals/de_DE/Merck-DE-Site/EUR/ViewProductDocuments-File?ProductSKU=MDA_CHEM-110263&DocumentType=APPL&DocumentId=200512.186.Appl&DocumentSource=GINAPPL | title=Application TCBS Agar (Vibrio Selective Agar) | work=[http://www.merckmillipore.com/ website of the [[Merck_KGaA|Merck KGaA]]] | accessdate=2013-03-18}}</ref>

